sequenceDiagram
    participant App as main()
    participant Sup as Supervisor
    participant FA as FileAgent
    participant MCP as MCP Server
    participant RA as ReportAgent
    participant LLM as Azure OpenAI

    App->>Sup: "Read file and generate report"
    Sup->>LLM: Which agent first?
    LLM-->>Sup: FileAgent

    Sup->>FA: readFile(path)
    FA->>LLM: message + MCP tool schemas
    LLM-->>FA: call read_file(path)
    FA->>MCP: read_file (stdio)
    MCP-->>FA: file contents
    FA->>LLM: tool result
    LLM-->>FA: file contents
    FA-->>Sup: stores "fileContent" in scope

    Sup->>LLM: What next?
    LLM-->>Sup: ReportAgent

    Sup->>RA: generateReport(fileContent)
    RA->>LLM: message with content
    LLM-->>RA: structured report
    RA-->>Sup: stores "report" in scope

    Sup-->>App: final report
